{"tid":2151760,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"【黃色音樂圈】暴動手足莊正出新歌《喝啖茶》請支持","createTime":"2020-08-11T14:23:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T09:40:37.000Z","uid":220798,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3c79837281de8167d82116a20a10419fe069e40a","tid":2151760,"uid":220798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T14:23:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qe55TeK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqe55TeK.jpg&h=3649158e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢係莊正。<br />\n<br />\n2019年莊正以個人身分出道，推出《開放世界》單曲，同年11月18日因涉嫌牽涉反修例運動被控暴動罪，2020年1月主動向公司提出解約，之後獨立身份推出探討社會事件的作品《Will (not) see you soon》。<br />\n<br />\n你未必認識佢，未必聽過佢嘅音樂作品，但作為同路人，佢至少值得你click入去聽一次佢嘅新歌、睇一次佢嘅mv。<br />\n<br />\n新歌：《喝啖茶》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QOTldEq7aBo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQOTldEq7aBo&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FiaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=cdaf6aae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QOTldEq7aBo</a><br />\n<br />\n作詞：莊正    作曲：莊正<br />\n編曲：YipYiuKwan@桃花猿<br />\n監製：YipYiuKwan@桃花猿<br />\n<br />\n(I just wanna live in this moment)<br />\n<br />\n若有苦惱喝啖茶<br />\n若有心事喝啖茶<br />\n若有鬱結喝啖茶<br />\n<br />\n若要諗嘢喝啖茶<br />\n若要釋放喝啖茶<br />\n若要抖下喝啖茶<br />\n<br />\n番工做嘢好撚忙 做到喊 攰到散<br />\n我想一切可以放慢<br />\n點解世界咁多困難<br />\n點解世界咁多嘢煩<br />\n<br />\n這個世界我看不慣<br />\n忙裡偷閑 抖下你咪話懶<br />\n放慢過 快活過 十五七秒既時間<br />\n飲啖功夫茶 繼續嘆<br />\n<br />\n放下重負去找到這寧靜<br />\n帶著內斂心感應這生命<br />\n世俗惱事 佢話要去適應<br />\n你咪適應<br />\n<br />\n若有苦惱喝啖茶<br />\n(放慢過)<br />\n若有心事喝啖茶<br />\n(快活過)<br />\n若有鬱結喝啖茶<br />\n(放慢過 快活過 飲啖功夫茶繼續嘆)<br />\n<br />\n若要諗嘢喝啖茶<br />\n(放慢過)<br />\n若要釋放喝啖茶<br />\n(快活過)<br />\n若要抖下喝啖茶<br />\n(放慢過 快活過 飲啖功夫茶繼續嘆)<br />\n<br />\n我唔係好識音樂，但覺得聽得好舒服，詞同mv都好有意思，係有誠意嘅作品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />會繼續g持，希望大家都會support莊正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ecc788a9b3f8ea9f21d811453f8779f1d6dd48c","tid":2151760,"uid":220798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T14:25:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"573999b94fa7ed6fa932c8f430f1fcc82130ea76","tid":2151760,"uid":220798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T14:25:36.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"c3edc90e5b2e619eef5ebb0ffe46d7ffa394e6d5","tid":2151760,"uid":240890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T14:26:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"121346d8e0b9d3dcb195ba60222b26cb0956a8b2","tid":2151760,"uid":124277,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T14:26:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e1e22ea4743fb3394a237f73daebfc90f2b2f498","tid":2151760,"uid":199332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T14:27:22.000Z","msg":"推 好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce435cdbd48c67a981097085c32ad3053a0dc8b2","tid":2151760,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T14:31:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c88eba86c1328f60c7da8cfd7da8ef7cb4bf4a6","tid":2151760,"uid":220798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T14:32:45.000Z","msg":"歌好聽，mv好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da03a6e70260b4cd2eb1bacada6dabd3f50a8303","tid":2151760,"uid":226573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T14:33:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0f951e917100df9dfadbe8f60